author: akarasulu
msg: Added code to now check if the producer class exists within the src/java
directory before creating one from scratch in the target/schema directory.
This is done to prevent collisions when static producers are hand woven which
is usually the case for anything which is not an AttributeType or ObjectClass

msg: XmlBean deserialization is now functional at least for fairly simple schemas.
Make sure to use the elementFormDefault="qualified" schema option since Axis will
force that anyhow and cause all sorts of namespace problems.
